overview: Frequencies are energy and energy is what we're all made out of, that's why we're all connected to every living thing, and to each other. 45min running time featuring: Bryce Young, Ryan Burch, Derrick Disney, Ari Browne, Ozzie Wright, Asher Pacey, Robin Kegel, Andy Nieblas, Gavin Beschen, Eric Snortum, and Rangi Ormond. Animations by Nanda Ormond. Art by Mitchell King. NAMELESS DIRECTION UNDERGROUND 2019
title: Zone Frequency
